::Prowl::

Prowl looks into Iron Raptor's eyes as his come level with hers, his love 
filled optics a bit dimm from the damage. His repair systems were still 
working on him, but they were beginning to take more energy than what they 
restored.

The room dimms for a second, threatening to black out. Prowl takes a few deep 
breaths and things come back into focus.

"I think I need a recharge," he says, going limp in her arms again.
